extendedInfo.description: Confused about the course? Confused about the institute?dbblr is an unique, educative and informative mobile application catering to the aspiring engineering student of Andhra Pradesh! Now that you have worked hard for EAMCET and itâs time for the counseling process. Using dbblr, you can make the most informed choice about the institution and course during EAMCET 2013 counseling. As the counseling process of EAMCET 2013 begins, it is very important to be informed about the institution that will shape your career.  Stay up to date on all the happenings around the counseling process.Apart from college information, dbblr provides you with a gamut of information on which course is the best suited for you, directly from leading industry experts along with the latest in news happening around EAMCET 2013Follow these 3 simple steps to make the wisest decision even during the mayhem of counseling:Step 1: Using the Rank based estimator figure out which colleges you are most likely eligible for based on EAMCET 2012 ranks.Step 2: Among the choice of colleges, choose the right one for you based on1) College profile, website2) Location of college 3) Admission fees4) BranchesStep 3: Using expert advice from engineering professors, decide which is the best branch for youThis application, along with the most recent fee structure, will provide you with the latest information related to various institutes and the EAMCET 2013 counseling process.
